    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and it's been such a joy to own. It's in really solid shape and has been well-loved, making it the perfect choice for anyone who wants a dependable car that still looks great pulling into the driveway. It runs like a dream and is totally ready for its next big adventure. If you're looking for a reliable companion for the road, this is the one! Feel free to give me a shout if you want to take it for a spin!",
      "price": 34500.0,
