    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, utilizing individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing to produce a linear power band up to its 8,000 RPM redline. The Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox offers precise shift gates, delivering power to the rear wheels via a M-Variable limited-slip differential. Recent preventative maintenance includes a comprehensive cooling system overhaul and a structural reinforcement of the rear subframe mounting points. The chassis retains its factory-tuned kinematics with MacPherson struts up front and a multi-link rear setup, providing exceptional turn-in and mid-corner stability. Finished in Carbon Black over Nappa leather, this example exhibits a light patina consistent with a well-sorted enthusiast driver.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 0
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
