    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This meticulously maintained sedan strikes the perfect balance between luxury and reliability. The exterior features a stunning Deep Charcoal Metallic finish that still holds a showroom-like luster, save for a few minor stone chips on the front fascia consistent with careful highway use. Inside, you\u2019ll find a pristine, smoke-free cabin appointed with premium black leather and brushed aluminum accents; the seats remain firm and supportive with only slight softening on the driver\u2019s side bolster. Every feature, from the intuitive navigation system to the dual-zone climate control, operates flawlessly. Mechanically, the car is in excellent health, boasting a full dealership service history, a recent oil change, and tires with approximately 70% tread remaining. It drives straight, shifts smoothly through all gears, and offers a quiet, composed ride. This is a turn-key vehicle for a discerning buyer who values a well-documented history and true pride of ownership.",
      "price": 36500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
