    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape\u2014super clean inside and out, and it runs like a dream! It\u2019s perfect for someone looking for a reliable car that\u2019s been well-loved and taken care of. You\u2019re going to love how smooth it feels on the road. Come take it for a spin!",
