    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a driver-focused example featuring the legendary S54 3.2L naturally aspirated inline-six, delivering a linear power band and an 8,000 RPM redline. The individual throttle bodies provide instantaneous throttle response, paired with a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission for total engagement. The chassis remains taut with upgraded polyurethane bushings and a reinforced rear subframe to mitigate structural fatigue. It benefits from a recent VANOS overhaul and rod bearing replacement, ensuring long-term mechanical reliability. Equipped with a factory limited-slip differential and staggered Style 67 wheels, this M3 maintains exceptional lateral grip and communicative feedback. While showing minor cosmetic patina consistent with its mileage, the drivetrain and suspension are dialed in for peak performance.",
